label: Cue Interval
tooltip: Time for which the fixation cross is visible (milliseconds)

label: Delay Interval
tooltip: Time from end of Cue Interval to presentation of stimuli (milliseconds)

label: Response Interval
tooltip: Time from beginning of stimulus presentation to response timeout (milliseconds)

label: Anti-Startle Interval
tooltip: Time from response input to beginning of Feedback Interval (milliseconds)

label: Feedback Interval
tooltip: Time for which feedback is visible (milliseconds)

label: Inter-trial Interval
tooltip: Time from end of Feedback Interval to next Cue Interval (i.e., beginning of next trial) (milliseconds)
